Package com.stasroshchenko.diploma.request

Class RegistrationRequest

java.lang.Object
com.stasroshchenko.diploma.request.RegistrationRequest
@PasswordMatchConstraint public class RegistrationRequest extends Object
Made for both encapsulating all client user's registration data, entered in Registration page form and sending this data as one object to controller. Has fields with validation constraints.

1.0
